      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642250/RenderMan_LiveState_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099624&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642250/RenderMan_LiveState_Solaris.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099624&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642268\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_LiveState_Solaris.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642250\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5440acc1-aa23-4c38-a811-10ddf6f41665\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p><br/></p><hr/><p><br/></p><p>Live Stats in Solaris allows you to inspect your Solaris scene.<br/><br/>To begin using Live Stats, you first need to attach the stats panel to a Render.  Simply press Attach Render and when you begin rendering the data will appear.<br/><br/></p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642250/RenderMan_Solaris_LiveStats.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099624&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642250/RenderMan_Solaris_LiveStats.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433099624&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642262\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LiveStats.jpg\" da